Griffin</b>, the late <b>Mica</b> and <b>Ahmet Ertegun</b>, <b>Lyor Cohen</=
b>, and <b>Max Carter</b>, a generationally talented vice chairman at Chris=
tie=E2=80=99s, who also happens to be the son of my friend <b>Graydon Carte=
r</b>.<br/><br/><i>Let=E2=80=99s get to it=E2=80=A6</i><br/><br/></p><ul st=
yle=3D"margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:16px;line-height:30px;margin-top:0;=
margin-bottom:0;list-style-type:square;mso-special-format:bullet"><li><i>Sa=
