=80=99ve been the best-performing bonds. So they=E2=80=99ve helped bond man=
agers outperform buying typical corporate bonds, but then with this upside =
in crypto.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>As always, this isn=E2=80=99t investment advic=
e. But if MicroStrategy=E2=80=99s stock continues its rocket-ship trajector=
y=E2=80=94it=E2=80=99s up<i> 678 percent</i> in the last year=E2=80=94thing=
s should work out just fine
